1. *Takvu* situaciju nikad ranije nisam doživeo. (I have never experienced such a situation before.)
2. Nisam očekivao *takvu* reakciju. (I didn't expect such a reaction.)
3. Ovi događaji su nas doveli do *takve* situacije. (These events have led us to such a situation.)
4. Živeo sam *takav* život. (I lived such a life.)
5. Ona je bila u *takvom* stanju. (She was in such a state.)
6. Nisam mogao da verujem *takvom* ponašanju. (I couldn't believe such behavior.)